trans-unit.source: Describes how to use the extension to import customers, vendors, items, and accounts from QuickBooks Desktop to Business Central.

seg-source.mrk: Describes how to use the extension to import customers, vendors, items, and accounts from QuickBooks Desktop to Business Central.

target.mrk: Popisuje jak používat rozšíření k importaci zákazníků, dodavatelů, zboží a účtů z QuickBooks Desktop do Business Central.

trans-unit.source: The QuickBooks Data Migration Extension

seg-source.mrk: The QuickBooks Data Migration Extension

target.mrk: Rozšíření QuickBooks Data Migration

trans-unit.source: This extension makes it easy to migrate customers, vendors, items, and accounts from QuickBooks to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: This extension makes it easy to migrate customers, vendors, items, and accounts from QuickBooks to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Toto rozšíření usnadňuje migraci zákazníků, dodavatelů, zboží a účtů z QuickBooks na [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: If your business uses QuickBooks today, you can export the relevant information and then open an assisted setup guide to upload the data to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: If your business uses QuickBooks today, you can export the relevant information and then open an assisted setup guide to upload the data to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Pokud vaše firma používá QuickBooks, můžete exportovat příslušné informace skrz průvodce asistovaného nastavení a poté data uložit do [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Importing Business Data from Other Finance Systems](across-import-data-configuration-packages.md).

seg-source.mrk: For more information, see [Importing Business Data from Other Finance Systems](across-import-data-configuration-packages.md).

target.mrk: Pro více informací navštivte [Import obchodních dat z jiných finančních systémů](across-import-data-configuration-packages.md).

trans-unit.source: Open documents for customers and vendors, such as invoices, credit memos and payments

seg-source.mrk: Open documents for customers and vendors, such as invoices, credit memos and payments

target.mrk: Otevřené dokumenty pro zákazníky a dodavatele, jako faktury, dobropisy a platby

trans-unit.source: We migrate only full amounts on sales and purchase documents.

seg-source.mrk: We migrate only full amounts on sales and purchase documents.

target.mrk: Migrujeme pouze plnou částku v prodejních a nákupních fakturách.

trans-unit.source: We do not update partially paid amounts.

seg-source.mrk: We do not update partially paid amounts.

target.mrk: Neaktualizujeme částečně zaplacené částky.

trans-unit.source: For example, if a customer has paid 300 of a total of 500 dollars on a sales invoice, we migrate the full 500.

seg-source.mrk: For example, if a customer has paid 300 of a total of 500 dollars on a sales invoice, we migrate the full 500.

target.mrk: Například, jestliže zákazník zaplatil 300, z celkových 500 korun na prodejní faktuře, migrujeme celých 500.

trans-unit.source: If you have received partial payments, you must update these manually, either before or after you migrate data.

seg-source.mrk: If you have received partial payments, you must update these manually, either before or after you migrate data.

target.mrk: Jestli jste obdrželi částečnou platbu, tak ji musíte aktualizovat manuálně, buď před, nebo po migraci dat.

trans-unit.source: We recommend that you apply outstanding transactions before you migrate, just to make things easier afterward.

seg-source.mrk: We recommend that you apply outstanding transactions before you migrate, just to make things easier afterward.

target.mrk: Doporučujeme abyste před migrací použili neuhrazené transakce, aby bylo možné později věci zjednodušit.

trans-unit.source: We do not migrate purchase orders or sales orders.

seg-source.mrk: We do not migrate purchase orders or sales orders.

target.mrk: Nemigrujeme nákupní a prodejní objednávky.

trans-unit.source: It's a good idea to plan this mapping before you migrate data.

seg-source.mrk: It's a good idea to plan this mapping before you migrate data.

target.mrk: Je dobrý nápad si toto mapování naplánovat před migrací dat.

seg-source.mrk: For example, the accounts where you post transactions for:

trans-unit.source: Adjustments in the general ledger

seg-source.mrk: Adjustments in the general ledger

target.mrk: Opravné položky v hlavní knize

trans-unit.source: Business Central requires that general ledger accounts have account numbers assigned to them.

seg-source.mrk: Business Central requires that general ledger accounts have account numbers assigned to them.

target.mrk: Business Central vyžaduje, aby měly účty v hlavní knize přiřazené čísla účtů.

trans-unit.source: Make sure that account numbers are assigned to your accounts in QuickBooks.

seg-source.mrk: Make sure that account numbers are assigned to your accounts in QuickBooks.

target.mrk: Ujistěte se, že čísla účtů jsou přiřazená k vašemu účtu v QuickBooks.

trans-unit.source: If transactions in QuickBooks have tax amounts, you must set up a tax account for your tax jurisdictions in Business Central before you can post transactions.

seg-source.mrk: If transactions in QuickBooks have tax amounts, you must set up a tax account for your tax jurisdictions in Business Central before you can post transactions.

target.mrk: Pokud mají transakce v aplikaci QuickBooks částky daně, musíte před zaúčtováním transakcí vytvořit daňový účet pro vaše daňové kompetence v aplikaci Business Central.

trans-unit.source: In order to get your data out of the QuickBooks desktop application you will need to download the Microsoft Data Exporter Tool.

seg-source.mrk: In order to get your data out of the QuickBooks desktop application you will need to download the Microsoft Data Exporter Tool.

target.mrk: Chcete-li získat data z desktopové aplikace QuickBooks, bude nutné stáhnout nástroj Microsoft Data Exporter Tool.

trans-unit.source: The instructions for the tool are in the Data Migration Wizard in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: The instructions for the tool are in the Data Migration Wizard in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Pokyny pro nástroj jsou v Průvodci migrací dat v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)]

trans-unit.source: The tool will connect to your QuickBooks application and export the applicable data to a .zip file.

seg-source.mrk: The tool will connect to your QuickBooks application and export the applicable data to a .zip file.

target.mrk: Nástroj se připojí k vaší aplikaci QuickBooks a exportuje příslušná data do souboru .zip.

trans-unit.source: Currently the data exporter tool only works with QuickBooks 2017 and 2018.

seg-source.mrk: Currently the data exporter tool only works with QuickBooks 2017 and 2018.

target.mrk: Nástroj pro export dat funguje v současné době pouze s QuickBooks 2017 a 2018.

trans-unit.source: Finding the QuickBooks Data Migration Extension

seg-source.mrk: Finding the QuickBooks Data Migration Extension

target.mrk: Vyhledání rozšíření QuickBooks Data Migration

trans-unit.source: The QuickBooks Data Migration extension is installed and ready to go as an integrated part of the Data Migration assisted setup guide.

seg-source.mrk: The QuickBooks Data Migration extension is installed and ready to go as an integrated part of the Data Migration assisted setup guide.

target.mrk: Rozšíření QuickBooks Data Migration je nainstalováno a připraveno k použítí jako integrovaná část asistovaného průvodce nastavením Data Migration.

trans-unit.source: If you are ready to get started now, and have exported your data from QuickBooks, choose the ![Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Tell me what you want to do") icon, enter **Assisted Setup**, and then choose the related link.

seg-source.mrk: If you are ready to get started now, and have exported your data from QuickBooks, choose the ![Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Tell me what you want to do") icon, enter **Assisted Setup**, and then choose the related link.

target.mrk: Pokud jste připraveni začít hned teď a exportovali jste svá data z QuickBooks, vyberte ![Žárovku, která otevře Řekněte mi funkci](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Řekněte mi co chcete udělat") ikona, zadejte **Asistované nastavení** a poté vyberte související odkaz.

trans-unit.source: Choose **Migrate business data**, and then follow the steps in the guide.

seg-source.mrk: Choose **Migrate business data**, and then follow the steps in the guide.

target.mrk: Vyberte možnost **Migrovat obchodní data** a poté postupujte podle pokynů v průvodci.

trans-unit.source: What do I do after I migrate Data?

seg-source.mrk: What do I do after I migrate Data?

target.mrk: Co mám dělat po migraci dat?

trans-unit.source: After you migrate data, transactions have the status Unposted, so you can review them and make adjustments.

seg-source.mrk: After you migrate data, transactions have the status Unposted, so you can review them and make adjustments.

target.mrk: Po migraci dat mají transakce stav Nezveřejněno, takže je můžete zkontrolovat a provést úpravy.

trans-unit.source: To review the transactions, go to the page where you would normally find them.

seg-source.mrk: To review the transactions, go to the page where you would normally find them.

target.mrk: Pokud chcete transakce zkontrolovat, přejděte na stránku, kde je obvykle najdete.

trans-unit.source: For example, to review unposted sales invoices, go to the Sales Invoices page.

seg-source.mrk: For example, to review unposted sales invoices, go to the Sales Invoices page.

target.mrk: Chcete-li například zkontrolovat nezveřejněné prodejní faktury, přejděte na stránku Prodejní faktury.

trans-unit.source: To review payment journals, go to the Payment Journals page.

seg-source.mrk: To review payment journals, go to the Payment Journals page.

target.mrk: Jestli chcete zkontrolovat deník plateb, přejděte na stránku Deník plateb.

trans-unit.source: There are a few things in particular that you should do: If the transactions in QuickBooks had markup or discount amounts, you must manually add the amounts to the related transactions in Business Central before you post them.

seg-source.mrk: There are a few things in particular that you should do:
If the transactions in QuickBooks had markup or discount amounts, you must manually add the amounts to the related transactions in Business Central before you post them.

target.mrk: Je zde několik věcí, které by jste měli zejména udělat:
Pokud transakce v aplikaci QuickBooks měly přirážku nebo slevu, je nutné je před zaúčtováním manuálně přidat do souvisejících transakcí v aplikaci Business Central.

trans-unit.source: If you are using value added tax (VAT), you may need to add a business posting group and a product posting group to the posting setup so that you can post VAT amounts.

seg-source.mrk: If you are using value added tax (VAT), you may need to add a business posting group and a product posting group to the posting setup so that you can post VAT amounts.

target.mrk: Pokud jste plátci DPH, budete možná muset do nastavení účtování přidat Obchodní účetní skupinu a Účetní skupinu zboží, abyste mohli účtovat DPH.

trans-unit.source: Verify the beginning balances for accounts in the general ledger.

seg-source.mrk: Verify the beginning balances for accounts in the general ledger.

target.mrk: Ověřte počáteční stavy pro účty v hlavní knize.

trans-unit.source: QuickBooks does not store the current balance for all accounts, so you might need to correct beginning balances.

seg-source.mrk: QuickBooks does not store the current balance for all accounts, so you might need to correct beginning balances.

target.mrk: QuickBooks neukládá aktuální stavy všech účtů, takže budete pravděpodobně muset opravit počáteční stavy.
